We see these stories every day.

77
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:15,838
Depression, anxiety, eating
disorders, self-harm

78
00:04:15,838 --> 00:04:18,383
these are just a few of the
prominent mental illnesses that

79
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:20,259
teens and young adults face.

80
00:04:20,635 --> 00:04:23,304
For many young people, these
conditions are an unexplained,

81
00:04:23,304 --> 00:04:26,391
confusing, and often paralyzing
part of their lives.

82
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:28,101
[Sarah] They can grow
 to believe

83
00:04:28,101 --> 00:04:29,477
