their fault.

84
00:04:29,477 --> 00:04:31,854
That this is something
they should be ashamed of.

85
00:04:31,854 --> 00:04:34,816
Sometimes they're too afraid
to reach out for help.

86
00:04:34,816 --> 00:04:38,152
Sometimes they're pressured to
hide this part of them away.

87
00:04:39,237 --> 00:04:41,155
