project as a small group

88
00:04:41,155 --> 00:04:42,448
of high school and
college students

89
00:04:42,448 --> 00:04:44,200
to tell our own stories and
those of our close

90
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,785
friends and family.

91
00:04:45,785 --> 00:04:49,580
We have seen first hand how easy
it is to hide behind a mask.

92
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:51,582
We wanted to start a
conversation.

93
00:04:51,582 --> 00:04:53,376
We put out a call asking for
teens to share

